headline: Ecolab: Great Business But Shares Are Priced Accordingly (Rating Downgrade)
summary: Ecolab has rebounded post-pandemic and remains a high-quality compounder, but its shares are now fully valued at a 36x P/E multiple. Read the latest analysis on the stock here.
